\[\mathbb{P}\left[\sum_{t=1}^{k}g_{t}\geq 0\right] =\mathbb{P}\left[\sum_{t=1}^{k}g_{t}+k\Delta\geq k\Delta\right]\] \[\leq\exp\left(-\frac{3k^{2}\Delta^{2}}{6k\Psi+2k\Delta}\right)\] \[\leq\exp\left(-\frac{k\Delta^{2}}{2\Psi+\Delta}\right).\]

